paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT *
FROM(
    SELECT orderDate
            ,Channel
            ,round((count(distinct case when shippedStatus='RTO' and rtoDate is not null then atb.subOrderId end))/(COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId)) * 100,2) as rto_percent
    FROM(
        SELECT orderDate,subOrderId,Channel       
        FROM `temp.order_sd`
        WHERE orderDate>='2023-04-01'
        ) atb
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                            ,shippedStatus
                            ,deliveredDate
                            ,rtoDate
            FROM `all(agCmDump)`
            ) ag
    ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
    
    GROUP BY orderDate, Channel
    ORDER BY orderDate
    )
",1000)

paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT *
FROM(
    SELECT orderDate
            ,Channel
            ,1-(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN deliveredDate is not null then atb.subOrderId else null end)/COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus = 'NA') THEN atb.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)) as rto_percent
    FROM(
        SELECT orderDate,subOrderId,Channel       
        FROM `temp.order_sd`
        WHERE orderDate>='2023-04-01'
        ) atb
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                            ,shippedStatus
                            ,deliveredDate
                            ,rtoDate
            FROM `all(agCmDump)`
            ) ag
    ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
    
    GROUP BY orderDate, Channel
    ORDER BY orderDate
    )
",1000)
